# Backup & Storage

## Borg
- Repo: nova-v2-backup op Storage Box
- Encryption: repokey-blake2
- Compression: lz4
- BORG_PASSPHRASE in /root/.nova_secrets (alleen op prod server)

## Cron
- 02:00 UTC daily op productie
- Script: /root/nova-backup.sh
- Logs: /var/log/nova-backup/

## Includes
- Postgres v1 + v2 dumps
- MinIO mirrors (alle buckets)
- N8n workflow exports
- Docker compose configs
- Docs directory (na agent 60)

## Retention
- 7 daily
- 4 weekly  
- 6 monthly

## DR Procedure
- Documented in docs/DR_PROCEDURE.md
- Target RTO: 4 uur
- Target RPO: 24 uur
- Drill tested: 193 tabellen restored in ~3 min
